short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Map Overlay  (for Rust:IO) for Barry's Rust Community Server

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a plugin that overlays the factions on Barry's Community Server onto the Rust:IO map. It can also be toggled within the page by using the link at the bottom.
